Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:05.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon, I'm sorry for lyin' to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:08.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Be good to Rikko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:58.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were acting odd last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:01.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the sneaking suspicion I had was spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.64,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.28,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let... go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:30.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:31.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not moving, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, you mean to go away for good, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:37.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to run off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:41.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning on leaving everyone and everything behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:48.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't be here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:54.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you become such a coward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:03:00.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the guy who told me,\N"Nothing good comes out of being afraid"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:05.66,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you guys doing this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.76,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Bon-ouji, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.90,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting about the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you're really into it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:26.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is I was scared too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:38.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,even if it's just one, let me stay like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:44.30,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko! Did you bring in today's paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:48.62,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I left it by the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.37,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:02.72,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.21,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:05.70,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.40,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.64,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring us anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:11.02,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, your hair's turned gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.31,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Has it? I suppose it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:15.14,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring presents?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.54,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I bought you stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.42,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.17,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:21.29,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, at least let him set foot in the house first.
