Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.29,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I'm sorry for being away all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.25,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,You look cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.20,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Nii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.00,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.13,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.38,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,...is for you, Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:47.29,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't know if you'll like it or not, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.40,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fountain pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.12,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, Nii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.79,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.91,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Something expensive like this is wasted on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:08.91,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,A child doesn't go turning down a present from his parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:15.25,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looks like everyone got a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.23,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko, pass these out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.03,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:27.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,A child and his parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming to practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:48.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:51.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Startin' today, I'm gonna practice my ass off for the festival.{maybe kill-for the festival}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:53.29,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:55.83,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.76,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,That was a weird way to greet each other.
