Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.92,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Me at the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:06.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was hoping that you would play bass for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.87,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.93,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Adults have a lot of things on their plate, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.88,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And there'd be so much to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.28,0:06:15.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:28.15,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:31.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no way we can lose now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.84,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.85,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,How's it goin' for you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.68,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're in the middle of getting our costumes fitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:59.81,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we're going to lose against you guys this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:02.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so flamboyant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We, on the other hand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...are plain. Way too plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any razzmatazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:15.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we might not be able to beat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.84,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:20.67,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,All we gotta' do is let our music do the fightin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:27.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but this is our last school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.51,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Easy to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.79,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But appealing to people who have no interest in jazz is a tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,There are still ten days left. We'll work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.58,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Rikko, if you're gonna refuse, now's the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause if you decide to do it,\Nwe're not gonna go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.05,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna sing, tell us right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:09.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But I hope you don't turn us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen's got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:14.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Would you help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:36.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.59,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kit-tens...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:51.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've got no swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:58.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Bright copper kettles and warm woolen mittens
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:05.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Brown paper packages tied up with strings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:13.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Cream colored ponies and crisp apple strudels
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Doorbells and sleigh bells and schnitzel with noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wild geese that fly with the moon on their wings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:23.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:27.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Girls in white dresses with blue satin sashes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Snowflakes that stay on my nose and eyelashes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:35.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Silver white winters that melt into springs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:38.84,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:48.89,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I simply remember my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:56.20,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And then I don't feel so bad
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,"My Favorite Things"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:05.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My{\i0} favorite things are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:09.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The footsteps of a certain person heading towards the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:13.35,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the piano and drums riffing in the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:15.90,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The laughter of two boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Silly, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:25.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Drums and watermelon and onigiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Those are a few of my favorite things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that, Sentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Bon. Your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us your "favorite things."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:43.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even before Ricchan said hers, I had something in mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:48.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My "favorite thing" is this time right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.68,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is playing our best at the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.51,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,how about playin' "Moanin'" one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.23,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, let's save it for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:14.55,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If we started jamming now, we wouldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow, then. Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:20.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:30.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He forgot to take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:34.04,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, you don't need a score for jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,An' I can just give it to him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:42.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:45.31,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna run to deliver something he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:49.42,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You might not be able to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
