Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:23.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.22,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.61,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.22,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.68,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:31.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:34.15,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.44,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.52,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.09,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He got into an accident on his motorbike last night
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,and was taken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:01.46,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.76,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.30,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.08,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.64,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro is... Sentaro is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:12.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the hospital to see how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here until I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:20.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:26.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've dashed down this slope countless times, but it's never felt this long.{\i0}
