Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.91,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you when it's your turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.15,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,so please get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.84,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.04,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,They've finished operating,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.22,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,but it's serious head trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.32,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He still hasn't regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:09.28,Letter,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\t(\fs33)\blur0.5\move(587,109,583,89)}No Visitors
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:08.32,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He might never wake up again,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.28,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,the doctor said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.16,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:13.30,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:20.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Even when Sen is all bloody from a fight, he just laughs it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:27.42,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Um... the one in there is Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:35.89,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but Nee-chan was riding on the back of Nii-chan's motorbike last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:38.49,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,They got hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Then how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:45.21,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,He's hurt, but not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.47,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,He was sitting over here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:56.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The place he's most likely to go...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...has gotta be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this angel before somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:15.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna take somebody to Heaven, could you make it me an' not Sachiko, angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:26.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I end up hurting the ones I most want to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:34.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why... was I even born?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Bon? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you cryin' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:54.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This way, we don't have to see each other cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:59.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "we"? I ain't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to cry, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:05.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've been keeping it bottled up all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:47.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:06.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the time, it looked like he was just stepping out...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:12.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but he disappeared, and the festival was over before it even began.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.78,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's Bon nii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, here. If you're able to eat these...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:27.54,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Sen nii-chan went?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:33.75,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Sen nii-chan would normally never give me a ride on his bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:40.05,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,But I had a twisted ankle and kept complaining about it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:43.43,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,The accident was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.67,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I have to apologize to Sen nii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:52.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchan, right now, if you focus on getting better,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.32,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro will come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You want to show him that you're healthy again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.71,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:08.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I said all that to Sacchan, but the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:15.17,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, what'll I do if Sentaro never comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:17.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ricchan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:23.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I bet when we least expect it, he'll suddenly turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have that feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.89,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.14,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He will come back, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:32.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.65,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, don't go anywhere, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:42.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:43.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:48.58,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I remember you. Bon-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.72,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know where he might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:55.12,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm afraid I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:01.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,he left this behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:08.89,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,He once told me the reason he always wore the rosary as a necklace was because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:16.33,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,he was afraid that if he lost it,\Nhe would be abandoned by the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Se—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:52.07,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe Sen had come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:21:01.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Pops, he's not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:06.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to practice with him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:09.61,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talkin' about, Bon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Never again...
